<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hoof" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hoof,</orth> the horny substance on the feet of horses: <bibl n="shak. ven 267" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 267</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 2, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.1.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 1, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.3.43" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.3.43" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.7.18" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 7, 18</bibl>. Used in contempt of the human foot: <cit><quote>plod away i' the h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.3.91" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 3, 91</bibl></cit> (F<hi rend="sub">2. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.3.91" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 3, 91</bibl> 4</hi> and M. Edd. <emph>o' the h.</emph>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>